name: Videos
descriptionHtml:
### Endpoint for creating new video record

Request payload must contain the following fields:

module: STRING,
video_steam_id: STRING

Request:

POST - https://apiqa.inquitech.in/api/v1/videos

raw 
  {
    "module": "Health",
    "video_stream_id": "BWUi6BS9T5Y"
}

Response:

400 - Bad Request 

  {"status":400,"status_type":"error","message":"Validation error","count":null,"data":null}
